<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="zh-Hant">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Infographic: Strategies for Feeding Exposure Models</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/chart.js"></script>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Noto+Sans+TC:wght@400;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Noto Sans TC', sans-serif;
            background-color: #F0F4F8; 
        }
        .chart-container {
            position: relative;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin-left: auto;
            margin-right: auto;
            height: 300px;
            max-height: 400px;
        }
        @media (min-width: 768px) {
            .chart-container {
                height: 350px;
            }
        }
        .flowchart-step {
            border: 2px solid #6B7280;
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            padding: 1rem;
            border-radius: 0.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 4px 6px -1px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 2px 4px -2px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
            transition: transform 0.2s;
        }
        .flowchart-step:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
        }
        .flowchart-arrow {
            font-size: 2rem;
            color: #4A5568;
            margin: 0 1rem;
            align-self: center;
        }
        .kpi-card {
            background-color: #FFFFFF;
            border-radius: 0.75rem;
            padding: 1.5rem;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1), 0 4px 6px -4px rgb(0 0 0 / 0.1);
        }
        .kpi-number {
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            line-height: 1;
        }
        .kpi-label {
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: #4A5568;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="text-gray-800">

    <div class="container mx-auto p-4 md:p-8 max-w-7xl">

        <header class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-[#0D47A1] mb-2">模式參數獲取策略</h1>
            <p class="text-lg font-bold text-red-600">如何有效獲取暴露評估模式的輸入數據</p>
        </header>

        <section class="mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1976D2]">核心挑戰：生成速率 (G) 的不確定性</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600">在所有模式輸入參數中，污染物生成速率(G)是最難準確估計的，也是模式預測準確性的最大變數來源。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="kpi-card bg-[#E3F2FD]">
                    <div class="kpi-number text-[#0D47A1]">G</div>
                    <div class="kpi-label">生成速率</div>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-gray-700">每單位時間釋放到空氣中的化學物質量。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-card bg-[#E3F2FD]">
                    <div class="kpi-number text-[#0D47A1]">β</div>
                    <div class="kpi-label">區域間空氣交換率</div>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-gray-700">近場(NF)與遠場(FF)之間的空氣交換速度。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="kpi-card bg-[#E3F2FD]">
                    <div class="kpi-number text-[#0D47A1]">Q</div>
                    <div class="kpi-label">整體通風率</div>
                    <p class="text-sm mt-2 text-gray-700">房間整體的換氣量。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1976D2]">策略層次：G值測定方法比較</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600">針對G值的不確定性，本章提出一個層次分明的策略框架，從低成本的保守估算到高精度的實驗室研究。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                <div class="chart-container h-96 md:h-[450px]">
                    <canvas id="methodsComparisonChart"></canvas>
                </div>
                <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">此圖表比較了三種主要方法在成本、準確度與數據需求上的差異，幫助職衛專家根據具體情境選擇最合適的策略。</p>
            </div>
        </section>
        
        <section class="mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1976D2]">決策流程：「以數據換取保守性」原則</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600">此原則提供了一個具成本效益的初步評估路徑。首先採用最保守的假設，如果結果安全，則評估完成；反之，則投入更多資源以獲取精確數據。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-center space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-4">
                <div class="flowchart-step w-full md:w-1/4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#0D47A1]">1. 採用保守假設</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">假設100%逸散、最長暴露時間、最低通風率。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flowchart-arrow">➔</div>
                <div class="flowchart-step w-full md:w-1/4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#0D47A1]">2. 計算暴露濃度</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">使用模式計算高估的暴露潛力。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="flowchart-arrow">➔</div>
                <div class="flowchart-step w-full md:w-1/4">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-[#0D47A1]">3. 與OEL比較</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">將計算結果與職業暴露容許限值進行比較。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
             <div class="flex justify-center mt-4">
                <div class="flowchart-arrow">↓</div>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-center items-stretch mt-4 space-y-4 md:space-y-0 md:space-x-8">
                <div class="flowchart-step w-full md:w-1/3 bg-green-50 border-green-500">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-green-700">低於OEL</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">情境可接受，記錄評估結果。無需進一步行動。</p>
                </div>
                 <div class="flowchart-step w-full md:w-1/3 bg-yellow-50 border-yellow-500">
                    <h3 class="font-bold text-lg text-yellow-700">高於OEL</h3>
                    <p class="text-sm">不代表不安全，需投入資源獲取更精確數據（如腔體研究），以降低估計值。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1976D2]">黃金標準：腔體研究</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600">腔體研究是獲取實證G值的終極工具。透過在受控環境中模擬作業，可以直接測量關鍵參數，並反推出精確的G值。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8 items-center">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-[#1976D2]">穩態濃度與G值求解</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">在腔體達到穩態後，可測量近場濃度($C_{NF,SS}$)，並利用以下公式反推生成速率(G)。</p>
                    <div class="bg-gray-100 p-4 rounded text-center text-lg font-mono">
                        C<sub>NF,SS</sub> = (G / Q) + (G / β)
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">其中 Q 和 β 可透過腔體通風系統和風速計直接測量，使 G 成為唯一未知數。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                     <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-center mb-4 text-[#1976D2]">達到穩態所需時間</h3>
                    <div class="chart-container h-64">
                        <canvas id="halfLifeChart"></canvas>
                    </div>
                    <p class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-4">達到穩態所需的時間取決於換氣率(k)。通常認為經過5個半衰期後系統即達到穩態。此圖顯示不同換氣率下達到穩態所需的時間。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1976D2]">模式的診斷力量：案例洞見</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600">當模式預測與實驗數據不符時，這往往指向未被發現的物理化學機制，突顯模式不僅是預測工具，更是科學發現的工具。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1976D2] mb-2">案例一：「洩漏的腔體」</h3>
                    <p class="font-semibold">發現：化學沉降效應 (Sink Effect)</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">示蹤氣體($CO_2$)的異常快速衰減，揭示了未塗漆牆板會吸收氣體。這說明室內表面可透過吸收、吸附或化學反應等非通風機制移除污染物。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#1976D2] mb-2">案例二：「消失的殺菌劑」</h3>
                    <p class="font-semibold">發現：表面介導的降解</p>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">模式必須加入「降解項」才能吻合實驗數據，最終發現殺菌劑在吸附到腔體玻璃表面後會發生氧化降解，這是在其原始基質中不會發生的。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="mb-16">
            <div class="text-center mb-8">
                <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-[#1976D2]">綜合結論：應對G值挑戰的策略框架</h2>
                <p class="mt-2 max-w-3xl mx-auto text-gray-600">本章針對生成速率(G)此一最大不確定性來源，提出一個層次分明的策略框架，為職衛專家提供一套完整的實務指南。</p>
            </div>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0D47A1] mb-2">1. 保守性估算</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">作為起點，提供快速、具成本效益的初步篩選評估，適用於低風險情境或資源有限的場合。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0D47A1] mb-2">2. 腔體研究</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">在高風險或需高精度數據的情境下，此方法是獲取準確、實證G值的黃金標準。</p>
                </div>
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg shadow-md p-6">
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#0D47A1] mb-2">3. 簡易實務實驗</h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 mt-2">對於多數日常應用，如質量平衡法等，能以最少資源投入，顯著降低G值的不確定性。</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </section>

        <footer class="text-center text-sm text-gray-500 mt-12 py-4">
            prepared by Peter Ho. 114.08.19
        </footer>

    </div>

    <script>
        const vibrantPalette = {
            blue: '#2196F3', 
            green: '#4CAF50',
            yellow: '#FFEB3B',
            orange: '#FF9800',
            red: '#F44336',
            purple: '#9C27B0'
        };

        function wrapLabel(str, maxWidth) {
            if (str.length <= maxWidth) {
                return str;
            }
            const words = str.split(' ');
            let lines = [];
            let currentLine = '';
            for (const word of words) {
                if ((currentLine + word).length > maxWidth) {
                    lines.push(currentLine.trim());
                    currentLine = '';
                }
                currentLine += word + ' ';
            }
            lines.push(currentLine.trim());
            return lines.filter(line => line);
        }

        const tooltipTitleCallback = function(tooltipItems) {
            const item = tooltipItems[0];
            let label = item.chart.data.labels[item.dataIndex];
            if (Array.isArray(label)) {
                return label.join(' ');
            } else {
                return label;
            }
        };
        
        const ctxMethods = document.getElementById('methodsComparisonChart').getContext('2d');
        new Chart(ctxMethods, {
            type: 'bar',
            data: {
                labels: ['保守性估算', '簡易實驗 (質量平衡等)', '腔體研究'],
                datasets: [{
                    label: '成本/精力',
                    data: [2, 4, 9],
                    backgroundColor: vibrantPalette.blue,
                    borderColor: vibrantPalette.blue,
                    borderWidth: 1
                }, {
                    label: '準確度',
                    data: [3, 7, 10],
                    backgroundColor: vibrantPalette.green,
                    borderColor: vibrantPalette.green,
                    borderWidth: 1
                },{
                    label: '數據需求',
                    data: [1, 5, 8],
                    backgroundColor: vibrantPalette.orange,
                    borderColor: vibrantPalette.orange,
                    borderWidth: 1
                }]
            },
            options: {
                responsive: true,
                maintainAspectRatio: false,
                indexAxis: 'y',
                scales: {
                    x: {
                        beginAtZero: true,
                        max: 10,
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '相對評分 (1=低, 10=高)'
                        }
                    }
                },
                plugins: {
                    title: {
                        display: true,
                        text: 'G值測定方法之多維度比較',
                        font: { size: 18 }
                    },
                    tooltip: {
                        callbacks: {
                           title: tooltipTitleCallback
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        });

        const ctxHalfLife = document.getElementById('halfLifeChart').getContext('2d');
        const k_values = [0.5, 1, 2, 4, 6, 8, 10];
        const t_half = k_values.map(k => 0.693 / k);
        const time_to_steady_state = t_half.map(t => t * 5);
        new Chart(ctxHalfLife, {
            type: 'line',
            data: {
                labels: k_values.map(k => `${k} ACH`),
                datasets: [{
                    label: '達到穩態所需時間 (小時)',
                    data: time_to_steady_state,
                    fill: false,
                    borderColor: vibrantPalette.purple,
                    tension: 0.1
                }]
            },
            options: {
                responsive: true,
                maintainAspectRatio: false,
                scales: {
                    y: {
                        beginAtZero: true,
                        title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '時間 (小時)'
                        }
                    },
                    x: {
                         title: {
                            display: true,
                            text: '每小時換氣次數 (k)'
                        }
                    }
                },
                plugins: {
                     title: {
                        display: false
                    },
                    tooltip: {
                        callbacks: {
                            title: tooltipTitleCallback
                        }
                    }
                }
            }
        });
    </script>

</body>
</html>
